  p Well, it&rsquo;s been long overdue a re-design for my home in the Internet. My last site was powered by <a href="http://wordpress.org">WordPress</a>, but since then I&rsquo;ve grown a lot as a developer. I&rsquo;ve learned to appreciate the power of simplicity and static assets. Besides, my WordPress site was slow as shit!

